items.text: jaffa! Pitches on a length around off stump and jumps at the batsman to beat the outside edge
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Moor, no run

items.text: length outside off, Moor looks to drive it on the up, gets beaten
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Moor, no run

items.text: slower one, on the pads, the batsman misses the flick, a big appeal for lbw but denied. Pitched outside leg, it seems. The batsmen collect a leg-bye in the meantime. Replays confirm it pitched well outside leg
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Moor, 1 leg bye

items.text: tossed up outside off, Moor goes up and over and clears the long-off fence
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Moor, SIX runs

items.text: length ball, just outside off, defended
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Moor, no run

items.text: a touch fuller on middle and leg, defended
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Moor, no run

items.text: length ball, pushed through, comes forward and defends
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Moor, no run

items.text: length ball, around middle, punched off the back foot towards long-on
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Moor, 1 run

items.text: length ball from around the wicket, Williams comes forward and blocks
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Williams, no run

items.text: length ball, outside off and going further away with the angle, Moor looks to drive it on the up, misses
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Moor, no run

items.text: back of length outside off, dabbed towards backward point
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Moor, no run

items.text: length ball, just around off, Moor was stuck in the crease, and gets beaten as he pushes at it
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Moor, no run

items.text: bouncer this time, but too wide outside off as Moor watches it go into the wicketkeeper's gloves
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Moor, 1 wide

items.text: full and wide once again, left alone
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Moor, no run

items.text: fuller outside off from around the wicket, driven through covers for a couple
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Moor, 2 runs

items.text: pitched up and driven past the mid-off fielder to end the over with a four
items.postText: It's time for drinks. Shashank will take you to the end of the match
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Moor, FOUR runs

items.preText: Hemant is all set to dig in to a lavish dinner spread. Hello all. Is there still some fight left in the game? Can these two take it close and then hit out?
items.text: slides back in from round the stumps, punched to long-on.
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Williams, 1 run

items.text: gets outside the line of the stumps and smothers this.
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Moor, no run

items.text: sharp turn, bounce from the rough to hit him on the upper right thigh.
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Moor, no run

items.text: disastrous decision to sweep a full delivery. Plumb in front. This was full, fired dead straight and once he was hit on the pad, only one decision it was going to be.
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Moor, OUT

dismissal.text: PJ Moor lbw b Mehidy Hasan Miraz 26 (45b 2x4 1x6) SR: 57.77

items.text: edged past slip, third man runs around to cut that off.
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Tiripano, 2 runs

items.text: hits this full toss straight back to the bowler.
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Tiripano, no run

items.text: slants a length ball back into the left-hander, tucked to fine leg. Mashrafe was running in very gently to deliver that
items.shortText: Mashrafe Mortaza to Williams, 1 run

items.text: nips back in from length outside off, defended.
items.shortText: Mashrafe Mortaza to Tiripano, no run

items.text: oh, dear. What on earth was Tiripano doing? Dabs it into the off side, and sets off for a run even though he saw his partner put his hand out to say no. Very good from Mahmud, who swooped in, picked up the ball and took a couple of steps towards the stumps before flicking an underarm throw to catch him short at the striker's end.
items.shortText: Mashrafe Mortaza to Tiripano, OUT

dismissal.text: DT Tiripano run out (Fazle Mahmud) 2 (4b 0x4 0x6) SR: 50.00
